{"tid":950130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鄭若驊物業僭建  律政司決定不檢控】","createTime":"2018-12-21T09:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T12:44:27.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56a1ba6f5bcd32b25433dd62fdd0f53bcbdcdccb","tid":950130,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊及其丈夫潘樂陶，在屯門海詩別墅物業被揭發僭建物的個案，刑事檢控專員決定檢控潘樂陶，但不檢控鄭若驊。<br />\n<br />\n刑事檢控專員梁卓然尋求外聘資深大律師蔡維邦的法律意見，認為沒有證據顯示4號屋的僭建物，是在鄭若驊購入後建造，或是她在成為業主後，明知而展開違例建築工程。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #律政司司長 #鄭若驊 #海詩別墅 #僭建 #刑事檢控專員"},{"pid":"59fa1fcd00bbd440ae7c9ee66cf22e1f84fc6b0a","tid":950130,"uid":38030,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"律政司決定不檢控律政司司長<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2079587bbf39fa49bfd8b5099d902fea51cbd6a7","tid":950130,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"僣建。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_SDaU49qrYY/Wl2rnzIXsDI/AAAAAAAATAE/fcyd3IxAQMgVvt63wlE3XKvycYFS2Qk7QCLcBGAs/s1600/cheng%2Bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-_SDaU49qrYY%2FWl2rnzIXsDI%2FAAAAAAAATAE%2Ffcyd3IxAQMgVvt63wlE3XKvycYFS2Qk7QCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fcheng%252Bb.jpg&h=e00cc1ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e95e05346f3bb1ef387131822eb5575a6d343773","tid":950130,"uid":8171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/yulun1978/1412318953-1411723015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fyulun1978%2F1412318953-1411723015.jpg&h=a01773ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d7b9f8dcaa804284c19fc388d67c909440f3582","tid":950130,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"中殖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji